====== H1157: בְּעַד (bᵉʻad) ======

===== Source =====

from  H5704  with prepositional prefix;

===== Meaning =====

in up to  or  over against ; generally  at ,  beside ,  among ,  behind ,  for , etc.

===== Definitions =====

  - in up to
  - over against
  - at
  - beside
  - among
  - behind
  - for

===== Usage =====

about, at by (means of), for, over, through, up (-on), within.
